               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) ʾOrit za-lǝdät “Genesis” (fols. 1ra-48vb), Gen. 1-2 is missing 
                     II) ʾOrit za-ḍäʾat “Exodus“ (fols. 49ra-87vb) 
 III) ʾOrit za-lewāwǝyān
                     “Leviticus” (fols. 88ra-119vb) 
 IV) ʾOrit za-ḫʷǝlqʷ “Numbers“ (fols.
                     120ra-151vb) 
 V) ʾOrit za-dagǝm “Deuteronomy” (fols. 152ra-195vb) 
                     VI) ʾOrit za-ʾIyasu “Joshua” (fols. 196ra-218vb) 
 VII) ʾOrit za-masāfǝnt
                     “Judges” (fols. 219ra-243rb), possibly incomplete 
 VIII) ʾOrit za-Rut
                     “Ruth” (fols. 243va-245vb).
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
