                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> Written in a fine secondary hand. The note states that Ms. belongs
                              to the church of ʾAdd Qʷälqʷal Qǝddus Giyorgis and mentions Tasfā
                              Ḥawāryāt as the commissioner of the Ms. and ʾEwosṭatiwos as the qes
                              gabaz. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- A few upper lines are left empty in the incipit pages of
                           all books, probably intended for receiving ornamental bands. 
 -
                           Writing exercises: <locus target="#33r">33r</locus>, 34r, 109r.</item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
                           <desc type="findingAid">- In Text VII there are unfilled spaces left for
                              rubrication.</desc>
